Package org.linuxforhealth.fhir.persistence.jdbc.util.type

Class NewNumberParmBehaviorUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linuxforhealth.fhir.persistence.jdbc.util.type.NewNumberParmBehaviorUtil
  • public class NewNumberParmBehaviorUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Number Parameter Behavior Util encapsulates the logic specific to Prefix treatment of the Search queries related to numbers, and the implied ranges therein. New implementation based on Select instead of StringBuilder
